Combien de clusters?

Pour étudier graphiquement quelle valeur de k nous donne la meilleure partition, nous pouvons tracer entre banseens et tot.withinss vs choix de k.

for(i in 1:10){
  
  # Pour chaque k, calcule entre etbetweenss et tot.withinss
  bss[i] <- kmeans(airline_without_text, centers=i)$betweenss
  wss[i] <- kmeans(airline_without_text, centers=i)$tot.withinss
}
grid.arrange(p3, p4, ncol=2)

k <-list()
for(i in 1:10){
  k[[i]] <- kmeans(airline_without_text,i)
}


betweennss_totss <- list()
for(i in 1:10){
  betweennss_totss[[i]] <- k[[i]]$betweenss/k[[i]]$totss
}

#type = b to say that we want it to
#be both dots and lines
plot(1:10,betweennss_totss,type="b",
     ylab="Between SS / Total SS",
     xlab = "Cluster(k)")

we notice that the best value of k is 3

DATA CLEANING

we notice that the aircraft has number after them we ll try to remove it

Aircrafts <- NULL
#select all the aircraft and cleaning them
for (i in 1:nrow(ana_delta_buissness)) {
  Aircrafts <- c(Aircrafts, b<-gsub("\\(.*", "", ana_delta_buissness$Aircraft.with.seatmap))
}
#Added a colom to the ana_delta
for (i in 1:nrow(ana_delta_buissness)) {
  ana_delta_buissness[i,10] <- Aircrafts[i]
}

CARACTERISATION DES CLUSTERS

Cluster 1 : this claster have the smallest planes with the lowest quality like E120 and ERJ-145 tunisair need to stay away from these planes that are in this cluster so cluster 1 is eleminated

Cluster 2 : this cluster have good planes that have the best qualities it deosnt have first class but the economy and buissness class are very excelent

Cluster 3 : this cluster is the most typical cluster with the presence of the 3 first classess eco buissness and first class plus this cluster have the highest number of planes , there is some bad planes like WG 80 but tunisair can use them for internal lignes

Cluster 4 : This cluster have only one plane witch is Airbus A319 VIP tunisair deosnt need those type of plane because they are very big ,very expancive and do long hault plus they need a high number of staff

profil typique
